{"word":"φονεύω","slug":"φονεύω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>φονεύω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <a href='S:φονεύς'><el>φονεύς</el></a>\n<el>(φονεύω,) ( φυτ. <el>-σω</el>) </el><p/><i>to murder, kill, slay</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>: —<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be slain</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/>"}]}